1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:02,400
I am serious about this.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,400
Sayuri is so cute
and important to me.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:09,300
I don't want to lose her.

4
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:11,000
Yui...

5
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:12,700
left.

6
00:00:12,710 --> 00:00:15,700
Yui was always finding me

7
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:17,600
and I couldn't find her.

8
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:22,000
What Christmas present would make Sayuri happy?

9
00:00:22,300 --> 00:00:24,700
Tiffany's double heart.

10
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,600
What do you want, Yui-chan?

11
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:29,600
Present from uncle-Santa.

12
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:39,500
