13
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,200
I don't have time to celebrate that!

14
00:00:42,700 --> 00:00:45,400
What are you doing for Christmas, Sayuri?

15
00:00:47,700 --> 00:00:49,700
It'll probably just be me and my dad.

16
00:00:49,900 --> 00:00:51,900
What? What about mom?
T/N: She means Madoka.

17
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,800
