21
00:01:06,650 --> 00:01:08,450
Don't make that face, manju.

22
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,100
Anko will leak out.

23
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:11,600
Oh no.

24
00:01:13,100 --> 00:01:13,900
Ow!

25
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:21,000
Eh~ Wouldn't it be nice if before Christmas
a cool guy moved to a house next door to me too.

