144
00:12:48,700 --> 00:12:51,200
Do your best in your exams.
Okay.

145
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:54,500
Can I open it?
Go on.

146
00:12:59,900 --> 00:13:00,700
What?

147
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:04,100
How did you know about this?

148
00:13:04,300 --> 00:13:05,700
