149
00:13:07,100 --> 00:13:07,900
Yui?

150
00:13:08,500 --> 00:13:12,500
Actually, I saw Yui-chan the other day.

151
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:17,500
Ah, but... I never told Yui that I wanted this.

152
00:13:17,700 --> 00:13:18,500
Is that so?

153
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:23,000
That's what she told me when she visited.

154
00:13:23,700 --> 00:13:25,700
She came when the restaurant was closed.

155
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:29,400
She came especially, to apologize.

156
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:34,800
She's a good girl, straightforward.

157
00:13:37,700 --> 00:13:41,200
That's right. She is, isn't she.

158
00:13:42,700 --> 00:13:46,700
And so, I also asked her.

159
00:13:47,800 --> 00:13:51,500
What she wants for Christmas.

160
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,000
And then?

161
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:57,750
She said...

162
00:14:00,300 --> 00:14:03,900
she wanted me to wish you a Merry Christmas.

163
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:41,000
Are you leaving?
Yeah.

164
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:46,000
Bring Yui-chan back home.

165
00:15:47,850 --> 00:15:48,850
Thank you.

166
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,000
Yui!

167
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:14,000
That hurts, Sayuri.

168
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:17,800
It's fine.

169
00:17:25,700 --> 00:17:27,650
I've hurt you so much.

170
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:30,900
I'm sorry.

171
00:17:33,700 --> 00:17:34,700
It's alright.

172
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:42,000
I missed you.

173
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:46,500
Yeah.

174
00:17:49,100 --> 00:17:52,400
I wanted to kiss you again.

175
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:54,500
Okay.

176
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:30,700
Prayer; Name: Shida Yui
May Sayuri find me some day.

177
00:18:31,800 --> 00:18:35,000
